data.description: A meticulously maintained home! The "Delano" is a darling rambler with a beautiful kitchen featuring a large "eat-in" island and a large great room with lots of windows, a spa "no step" shower in the primary bathroom, and upgraded flooring throughout! SpringHouse Village is a 55-and-better community with a significant emphasis on Active-Adult, Resort-Style living! This community has it's own full-time lifestyle director dedicated to curating a calendar each month full of fun activities and clubs to participate in! With a huge 10,000 + Sqft clubhouse, everything you could want is just steps away! You might wonder, "How am I going to have enough time to enjoy all of these amenities?". Well, SpringHouse Village frees up your time by taking care of all snow removal and landscaping for you! Come see yourself living here! Attention VA Buyers!!! -Assumable 2.75% VA loan.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county website .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
